# ─── Pipeline & repo config ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Only core maintainers may change CI workflows, CODEOWNERS, or cliff config.
/.github/                    @uqal-lang/maintainers
/cliff.toml                  @uqal-lang/maintainers

# ─── All modules ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Every module PR requires at least one maintainer approval.
/modules/                    @uqal-lang/maintainers

# ─── Module-specific owners ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Added when a module is first merged. The listed author can approve their own
# module's future PRs without needing an additional maintainer review,
# as long as a maintainer has already approved the initial submission.
#
# Format:
#   /modules/community.<name>/   @uqal-lang/maintainers @github-handle
#
# Example (uncomment and fill in after first merge):
# /modules/community.postgis/    @uqal-lang/maintainers @contributor-handle
